#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
   int T,ax,ay,bx,by,cx,cy,dx,dy;

   for(scanf("%d",&T);T;T--)
   {
       scanf("%d %d %d %d",&ax,&ay,&bx,&by);
       scanf("%d %d %d %d",&cx,&cy,&dx,&dy);

       if((bx<cx) || (bx>cx && by<cy) || (bx>cx && dy<ay))
         {  printf("No Overlap\n");
           continue;}
    
      if(ax<cx && ay<cy)
         printf("%d %d %d %d\n",cx,cy,bx,by);
      if(ax<cx && ay>cy)
        printf("%d %d %d %d\n",cx,ay,bx,dy);
      if(cx<ax && cy<ay)
        printf("%d %d %d %d\n",ax,ay,dx,dy);
      if(cx<ax && cy>ay)
       printf("%d %d %d %d\n",ax,cy,dx,by);
      }
   return 0;
 }
